sources.description: Born to Kill (released in the U.K. as Lady of Deceit and in Australia as Deadlier Than the Male ) is a 1947 RKO Pictures American film noir starring Lawrence Tierney , Claire Trevor and Walter Slezak with Esther Howard , Elisha Cook Jr. , and Audrey Long in supporting roles. The film was director Robert Wise 's first film noir production, preceding his later work on The Set-Up (1949) and The Captive City (1952).
